  "title": "Custom Background HD",
  "description": "Change your Minecraft menu background with any image of your choice",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/684/717/cbf4e971-7207-4602-bd76-b44081f9b7df.png\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/760/15/custom-background-hd.png\" width=\"1125\" height=\"78\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Resource Pack-HD-green?style=plastic\" /> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/buy me a coffee-support-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/uCPfPBvsRJ\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/870825743788158986?color=blue&amp;style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GamerPotionDev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/my other-projects-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/get%20a%20server-click%20here-blue?style=plastic\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Summary</span></p>\n<p>Custom Main Menu background resource pack created for use on my <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/darkrpg\">DarkRPG</a> modpack. Now released as a standalone.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Description</span></p>\n<p>This will further improve your vanilla experience by allowing you to change your Main Menu background to anything of your choice.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Simply download this resource pack and apply it for a custom main menu background.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To change the background</p>\n<p>- Get a PNG screenshot or HD image from anywhere and overwrite the following file inside the zip file. <em>Custom Background HD.zip / assets / minecraft / textures / gui / title / background /&nbsp;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">panorama_overlay.png</span></em></p>\n<p>- Make sure your background image is renamed to 'panorama_overlay.png'&nbsp;</p>\n<p>- Apply the resource pack and you can enjoy a custom main menu background</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Image background source -&nbsp;https://pixabay.com/illustrations/fire-and-water-hands-fight-fire-2354583/</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/760/12/2023-11-16_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"633\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/760/13/2023-11-16_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"633\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/760/14/2023-11-16_10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"633\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/434/158/dec51e74-03ba-4abb-920c-bdc47a4e302a.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/brandasset/kofi_bg_tag_dark.png\" width=\"341\" height=\"129\" /></a></p>",
